SF / Bay Area — 24 full-time roles at Atlassian, makers of JIRA and Confluence, Stash and Bitbucket, and more.

We're hiring a lot of great people. Our software for software developers is used by over 23,000 organizations. If you can dream it; JIRA and Confluence, Bamboo and Bitbucket help you plan it, build it, and launch it. Yes, there's 24 open roles in SF: http://atlassian.com/company/careers/?tab=sf ...such as

Product Marketing — JIRA;
Product Marketing — Developer Tools;
Product Manager — Marketplace;
Dev Team Lead — Bitbucket;
Developer Advocate;
Web Developer;
Technical Writer;
and about 17 more.

Dogs are welcome. Beer is free. And there's 450 other passionate hackers and doers in a fast-growing company. Wanna join?
